item.title: CVE-2023-0150|2023-03-17T08:55:00.811Z -- unknown -- cloak%20front%20end%20email
item.description: The Cloak Front End Email WordPress plugin before 1.9.2 does not validate and escape some of its shortcode attributes before outputting them back in a page/post where the shortcode is embed, which could allow users with the contributor role and above to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks
